Module com.example.schedulingsystem
Package Class

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
Class.Appointment
public class Appointment extends Object
This is the appointment class! This class holds each appointment's data such as appointment id, title, description, location, type, start timestamp, end timestamp, create data timestamp etc.
